                    <p>
                     <em>
                      <strong>
                       The Shanghai Jews: Risk and Resilience in a Refugee Community
                      </strong>
                     </em>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     Exhibit opens January 15.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     The two-day conference will be held on March 13–14. For the list of participants and a full schedule of the programs click on the link
                     <a href="https://ccjs.uchicago.edu/shanghai-jews-event-0">
                      <u>
                       here.
                      </u>
                     </a>
                    </p>
