                  <div class="views-field views-field-body">
                   <div class="field-content">
                    <p>
                     Second-year student in the College, Jonah Lubin, takes on the role of the editorial assistant for the Yiddish journal
                     <em>
                      In Geveb.
                     </em>
                     Read more
                     <u>
                      <a href="https://ingeveb.org/blog/introducing-jonah-lubin-editorial-intern">
