                   <div class="field-content">
                    <p>
                     Congratulations to longtime Center supporter, June Patinkin, Class of 2018. Mrs. Patinkin and her late husband, Harold (Hal), endowed a visiting professorship that has brought to campus important scholars including Raymond Cohen, Ilana Pardes, Anat Feinberg, and Raphael Greenberg. Read more
